## Usage examples

### images

Get all availables images:

```bash
sandbox-cli images
```

```bash
┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
